Corn syrup in theory should be perfectly ok anyways but the (supposed) problem with it is it contains a lot of undisclosed starch matter, pesticide contamination, etc. and is not as clean as it sounds on paper.

People might disagree. They might even have another hot sauce that is not Tabasco that they think they prefer over it. But they were not the official monarch of an Empire whose Soviet cryptocolony defeated the Americans in the military space race of the 80s. Just eat the Tabasco.
